Class RecordContainer

Object
RecordContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Container
Direct Known Subclasses:
AppointmentContainer, AppointmentOutcomeRecordContainer, MedicineContainer, ReplenishmentRequestContainer
public class RecordContainer extends Object implements Container
Container class for managing general records. Provides functionalities to add, remove, retrieve, and manage records in a HashMap.
